{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic| name=Relashio| type=[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic#Spells|Spell]] (Charm)| features=Releasing an object| appearance=[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Books/Goblet of Fire/Chapter 26|Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire]] }}
== Overview ==
'''''Relashio''''' is a spell that is used to release an object from another object that is binding it, like chains.
== Extended Description ==
{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Beginner Spoiler}}
If used underwater, this spell creates a jet of boiling water. [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Characters/Harry Potter|Harry]] used this spell underwater when he is attacked by [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic/Grindylow|Grindylows]] in [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Books/Goblet of Fire/Chapter 26|Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire]] as a part of the Second Task.
