==History of Structural methods== The initial pargraph makes it sound as if no model building work was done at all in the early 80's due to a lack of computing power. That's misleading. It was just much more expensive, less automated and at a less advanced stage. Evans and Sutherland's machines were being used for enzyme models and to guide choices in synthesis of variant inhibitors. [[User:JamesCrook|JamesCrook]] ([[User talk:JamesCrook|talk]]) 11:22, 31 October 2010 (UTC)
